    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752760/extras/0d3982f21579d9bf13f169aa78d81ea0.avif?t=1738900273\" width=621 height=113 /></span><br><br>Soulstopia Φ is a wave-based action arcade game where you set the ill-fated free using various attacks!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752760/extras/495129e17363d01399a48fd972e38e35.poster.avif?t=1738900273\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752760/extras/495129e17363d01399a48fd972e38e35.webm?t=1738900273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752760/extras/495129e17363d01399a48fd972e38e35.mp4?t=1738900273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752760/extras/36c8806adf7fc502643e41d90d78a717.avif?t=1738900273\" width=621 height=113 /></span><br><br>A realm between heaven and hell, a stopping point for those at-odds with their demise. Suddenly pulled out of their lives, these restless spirits arrived in Soulstopia — to be set free by a lonesome maiden.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752760/extras/1b43e3a0dc7f329015f56a30e81317bc.poster.avif?t=1738900273\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752760/extras/1b43e3a0dc7f329015f56a30e81317bc.webm?t=1738900273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752760/extras/1b43e3a0dc7f329015f56a30e81317bc.mp4?t=1738900273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752760/extras/6d6aa763a44f55ec3d912df9e7593694.avif?t=1738900273\" width=621 height=113 /></span><br><br>▸A combat system with various options.<br>▸Five stages where you slice through waves of enemies.<br>▸Story scenes displayed in a visual novel format.<br>▸Journal entries that provide more insight into the world.<br>▸Color customization featuring nine unique palettes.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752760/extras/dad53fdc47c0571ae412d338fd82fbed.poster.avif?t=1738900273\" width=600 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752760/extras/dad53fdc47c0571ae412d338fd82fbed.webm?t=1738900273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752760/extras/dad53fdc47c0571ae412d338fd82fbed.mp4?t=1738900273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752760/extras/73128ee7e19d88f851c34165a48da48f.avif?t=1738900273\" width=621 height=113 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752760/extras/7790d010d2d5b1faa556cf4dccc3c26d.avif?t=1738900273\" width=607 height=754 /></span>",
